### List sales
GET https://localhost:5001/api/Sales?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Create sale
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "saleNumber": "S-1001",
  "customerId": "CUST-002",
  "customerName": "Maria Souza",
  "branchId": "BR-001",
  "branchName": "Filial Centro",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "PRD-001",
      "productName": "Cerveja Pilsen",
      "quantity": 6,
      "unitPrice": 5.50
    }
  ]
}

### Cancel sale
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/sales/S-1001
